	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a <a href="http://pineight.com/nes/meece.nes" class="postlink">demo</a> in case anyone wants to start trying to emulate this.
<br />
<br />Port 1: NES or Super NES Controller
<br />Port 2: Super NES Mouse
<br />
<br />Pressing B (NES Controller) or Y (Super NES Controller) changes the mouse's sensitivity.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
